<h2 id="section-top">Facilities</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel three-sm">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p>A range of shopping, eating, banking, entertainment and spiritual care services are available on this site. Please see http://www.guysandstthomas.nhs.uk/pandv/facilities/guysfacilities.aspx for a full list.</p>
</div>
